    Verse: 9
Tags:
  - Here & Now
---
Today is, for all that we know, the opportunity and occasion of our
lives. On what we do or say today may depend the success and completeness
of our entire life-struggle. It is for us, therefore, to use every moment
of today as if our very eternity were dependent on its words and deeds.
